    //   - PDF/UA-1 (self-check) = post-export structural assertions on the
    //                              exported bytes (StructTreeRoot, MarkInfo,
    //                              orphaned leaves, /Scope, /ActualText, /Alt,
    //                              font embedding, encryption, etc.)
